// Keypath:
// Keypath: foo
// Keypath: foo.bar
// Keypath: foo.bar.baz  If the keypath is a mapping, it will be adjusted relative to the originating instance's root data context. This is what primarily sets  @rootpath  apart from  @keypath .   Ractive.components.Message = Ractive.extend({
  data: () =  ({
    info : {},
  }),
