(Object string, boolean )  A map of elements that controls whether or not interpolation is allowed within the element. If an element is present in the map, then nested tags are treated as text rather than elements, as in a  script  tag. If the value associated with the element is  false , mustaches within the element are also treated as text rather than blocks or interpolators.  interpolate: {
