   frame Am I a bad element or just misunderstood? /frame 
`,
sanitize: true

// result:
//  p some content /p   The object form should have  elements  which is an array of blacklisted elements and  eventAttributes  boolean which, when  true , also strips out event attributes.  template: `
   p some content /p 
   div onclick= doEvil() the good stuff /div 
`,
sanitize: {
  elements: [ 'p' ],
  eventAttributes: true
}

// result:
//  div the good stuff /div

(Array[string])  Sets the static (one-time binding) delimiters. Defaults to  [ '[[', ']]' ] .  var ractive = Ractive({
