(string|array|object|function)  The template to use. Must either be a CSS selector string pointing to an element on the page containing the template, an HTML string, an object resulting from  Ractive.parse()  or a function that returns any of the previous options. The function form accepts processed  data  and a Parse Object.  // Selector
